parameters: This time... I have to give you this cellphone...

I don't think it will be like last time... but I'm a little
scared...
Hinata Aki: I found Uncle's cellphone near here, you know...
Hinata Aki: I thought I should return it to you...
Hinata Aki: Ah... Ah... U-uncle... U... U... You...

Sayama: Wait, wait!! I'm putting on my pants!! Don't shout so
loudly!!
Hinata Aki: Ahaha... Don't worry about it...

Hinata Aki: This cellphone... it's the one that the old man
dropped, right?
Sayama: My cellphone...! Did my sister find it for me?

Sayama: Thank goodness...! I was in trouble because I couldn't
find it no matter where I looked.
Hinata Aki: Oh, I see~ That's good then!
Sayama: This cellphone has a lot of old photos in it, you know~
\N <Hinata Aki> I accidentally saw the screen...

Hinata Aki: The person on the screen... looks just like me,
doesn't it?
Sayama: Ah... this child... is my daughter.
Hinata Aki: Daughter...!? Uncle, are you married!?
Sayama: It was a long time ago...
Sayama: My daughter occasionally comes to check on me.
Sayama: Well... the frequency has been decreasing though...

Sayama: So when I met my sister, I thought she brought a man
with her and that my daughter came to check on me...
Sayama: I... accidentally teased you... I'm sorry...

Sayama: I mistook my daughter's face... and ended up sexually
harassing my sister. I'm really pathetic...

Hinata Aki: You thought I was your daughter and said something
like sexual harassment to me!?
Sayama: Ah... Am I really weird after all?
Hinata Aki: ...Uncle, you're going to be disliked.

Sayama: Ugh... I was scolded by my daughter too... I'll be more
careful...
Hinata Aki: ...It's better not to sleep naked!
Hinata Aki: Because it's a promise...!

Hinata Aki: ...Alright! I've given you my phone, so I'll be
heading home soon.

Sayama: Are you already leaving...? You should take your time
and relax a bit more, you know?

Sayama: Well, come again... It feels like I'm talking to my
daughter, so it's nice.
Hinata Aki: Ahaha~ Whenever I feel like it!
